# Next.js Frontend Rules

- Import types/schemas from `@writer-mentor-ai/shared` only — never apps/api
- Hooks in `src/lib/hooks/use-<feature>.ts` using TanStack Query
- API calls via `@/lib/api/client` apiFetch helper
- Forms: React Hook Form + shared Zod schemas
- UI: shadcn/ui components in `src/components/ui/`
- Pages in App Router `src/app/`
- Ask user for route path if not specified
